-1 win over Sampdoria before the three-week winter break in Italy. December 30, 2018 In "Sports" Fabio Quagliarella joined Cristiano Ronaldo at the top of the Serie A scoring charts on Sunday as his brace took him to 19 goals for the season and kept Sampdoria in a tight race for European football next season. March 3, 2019 In "Sports"